paragraphs.title: Dickey–Fuller test
paragraphs.text:
val r = realisations(0)
val X = r.datapoints.dropRight(1).map(_.value)
val Y = for(i <- 0 until r.datapoints.length - 1) yield r.datapoints(i + 1).value - r.datapoints(i).value
val nSumXY = X.length * (for(i <- X.indices) yield X(i) * Y(i)).sum
val mulSumXSumY = X.sum * Y.sum
val nSumX2 = X.length * X.map(scalaPow(_, 2)).sum
val sumX2 = scalaPow(X.sum, 2)
